    <div class="content">
      <h1>Hey, <span>Wonderful</span> to Meet You</h1>
      <div class="images">
        <img src="../assets/1717443476396.jpg" alt="Ali Raza" />
        <img src="../assets/IMG-20231204-WA0005.jpg" alt="Ali Raza" />
        <img
          src="../assets/WhatsApp Image 2025-03-03 at 10.36.58 AM.png"
          alt="Ali Raza"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="aboutDesc">
        <p>
          By 2023, I began turning my curiosity for the web into something real.
          What started as a personal blog—just me, Ali Raza, sharing thoughts on
          tech, code, and creativity—slowly began reaching others who shared the
          same passion. I poured hours into learning, designing, and building
          everything from scratch. Over time, the blog gained traction, and in a
          defining moment, I landed my first collaboration with a regional tech
          brand. That was the push I needed. As a solo developer and founder, I
          continued refining the platform—writing, coding, and managing every
          piece myself. Eventually, I hosted a small community event to share my
          journey and help others starting out. That moment reminded me why I
          started: with consistency, curiosity, and a keyboard—anything is
          possible.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
          <i class="fas fa-rocket fa-xl" style="color: orangered"></i>
          <h1>Empowering Innovation</h1>
          <p>
            I consistently push the boundaries of technology, leading to unique
            and effective solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt fa-xl" style="color: blue"></i>
          <h1>Community-Centric Approach</h1>
          <p>
            My commitment to giving back not only enhances their reputation but
            also strengthens ties within the community..
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line fa-xl" style="color: green"></i>
          <h1>Flexibility & Adaptability</h1>
          <p>
            I'm agile work environment allows them to quickly adapt to changing
            market needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
